1.1. Personal Information: When you create an account or use certain features of our App, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and profile picture. This information is necessary to provide you with a personalized experience and facilitate bookings.

1.2. Service Requests: When you book a service through our App, we collect information related to the specific service requested, such as service type, preferred date and time, and project details. This information is essential for connecting you with the right service providers.

1.3. Usage Data: We may collect information about how you interact with our App, including pages visited, features used, and other activities. This helps us improve our App and provide you with a seamless experience.

2. How We Use Your Information

2.1. Provide Services: We use your personal information to facilitate service bookings, connect you with service providers, and ensure a smooth user experience.

2.2. Communication: We may use your contact information to send important updates, confirmations, and notifications related to your bookings.

2.3. Improve Our App: Your usage data allows us to analyze App performance, identify areas for improvement, and enhance our services.

2.4. Customer Support: We may use your information to respond to your inquiries, troubleshoot issues, and provide customer support.

2.5. Personalization: With your consent, we may use your data to offer personalized recommendations, promotions, and content tailored to your interests.

3. How We Protect Your Information

3.1. Data Security: We implement security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.

3.2. Secure Payments: For payment processing, we use trusted third-party payment providers who adhere to industry standards for data security.

4. Data Sharing

4.1. Service Providers: We may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in delivering our services, such as payment processors and customer support partners.

4.2. Legal Compliance: We may disclose your information when required by law or to protect our legal rights, enforce our Terms of Service, or respond to a legal request.

5. Your Choices

5.1. Account Management: You can review and update your account information at any time through the App settings.

5.2. Marketing Communications: You can opt-out of receiving promotional emails or notifications from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in the emails or adjusting your notification settings.

6. Children's Privacy

Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we learn that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child, we will promptly delete it.

7. Updates to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes through the App or via email.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at thisisaayushbaniya@gmail.com.

Thank you for choosing Helpmandu. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to safeguarding your personal information.
